	<div id="colOne">
3D-footprint is a database of DNA-binding protein structures that is updated weekly with <a href="http://www.rcsb.org/pdb">Protein Data Bank</a> complexes, providing:
	<ul>
                <li>structure-based binding specificities and sequence logos</li>
                <li><a href="./SCOPtree.html">classification</a> and  <a href="./clusters.html">clusters</a> of protein-DNA interfaces</li>
                <li><a href="./download.html">downloads</a> / <a href="./stats.html">stats</a></li>
		<li><a href="./weekcomplex.html">complex of the week</a></li>
		<li><a href="./tutorial.html">tutorial</a></li>
	</ul>
	<strong>Tools:</strong>
	<ul>	
		<li><a href="./footprint.html">footprint</a> your structure</li>
		<li><a href="./miner.html">consensus miner</a></li>
	</ul>
